Class PaymentHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.strohalm.cyclos.webservices.utils.PaymentHelper

  • public class PaymentHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class for web services payments
    WARN: Be aware that this helper doesn't access the services through the security layer. They are all local services.

    luis
